外帶的蛋糕直接算了服務費。\\n明明是跟朋友分開結帳，店家當場還包了外帶的蛋糕給我，所以店家顯然是有意的，沒有任何說明的情況下，就報了一個總金額給我。直到離開店以後才發現被多收錢，非常不舒服。\"},{\"rating\":5,\"time\":\"2025-04-10T14:15:51.000Z\",\"text\":\"義大利麵只有一種可以選擇，但真的蠻好吃的，披薩皮很薄脆，烤得剛剛好，少數遇到連店裡面的水都要收錢，但$30可以買一大瓶礦泉水也是少見。\"},{\"rating\":3,\"time\":\"2025-05-01T03:13:11.000Z\",\"text\":\"比薩還行\\n紅蘿蔔蛋糕$100算便宜也不錯\\n調酒味道很淡\\n綜合拼盤份量偏少\"},{\"rating\":5,\"time\":\"2025-05-03T03:14:38.000Z\",\"text\":\"肋眼牛排的肉質不錯，\\n自身是不怕牛油的部分，\\n只可惜牛油的比例也太高了，\\n同行友人那塊牛排接近1/4都是油。\\n配餐的薯泥不錯吃。\"}],\"photoInformation\":\"共 10 張照片，成功辨識 2 張菜單圖片。菜單內容：1$20\\nDeanston\\n-Dalmore 15 P\\n-Dalate Ci\\n-Dalmore Part\\n-Glengan 18\\n-Glenght Le\\n-The Believe\\n-Abelour Cash\\n-Aberlour 16.\\n\\n1.凱撒沙拉 Caesar Salad.\\n2. 凱撒雞肉沙拉 Chicken Caesar Salad\\n3. 希臘式田園沙拉 Greek Salad\\n4.酪梨烤雞肉沙拉 Chicken and Avocado Salad\\n5. 牛肉菲力沙拉 Filet Salad\\n180$\\n260$\\n200$\\n-300$\\n----\\n400$\\n1.美式辣味雞翅+薯條Spicy chicken wings + fries 8 售240$\\n2.The Park雞塊+薯條 Chicken nuggets + fries 180$\\n3. 香脆薯條 Fries\\n4.全部來大拼盤 Mix basket\\n150$\\n400$\\n5. 加拿大肉汁奶酪薯條 Fries with cheese and gravy...250$\\n328\\n經典牛肉紅醬義大利麵 210$ 紅蘿蔔蛋糕\\n100$\\nSp...\",\"name\":\"The Park\",\"summary\":\"\",\"types\":\"餐廳\",\"priceInformation\":\"中等\",\"extraInformation\":\"外送 / 內用 / 可預約 / 提供啤酒 / 葡萄酒 / 外帶\"}]","genkit:state":"success"},"displayName":"restaurantRawToRestaurantInput","links":[],"instrumentationLibrary":{"name":"genkit-tracer","version":"v1"},"spanKind":"INTERNAL","sameProcessAsParentSpan":{"value":true},"status":{"code":0},"timeEvents":{"timeEvent":[]}},"b479242a1a30cc40":{"spanId":"b479242a1a30cc40","traceId":"deadb9b43d8e9734d3c18061a2595a98","parentSpanId":"2f52b5bd8e03ab4f","startTime":1749270111274,"endTime":1749270114829.2188,"attributes":{"genkit:type":"action","genkit:metadata:subtype":"model","genkit:name":"vertexai/gemini-2.0-flash","genkit:path":"/{restaurantRecommendation,t:flow}/{findRestaurants,t:flow}/{generate,t:util}/{vertexai/gemini-2.0-flash,t:action,s:model}","genkit:input":"{\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"cont